	nav.navbar.navbar-default.navbar-fixed-top
		.container-fluid.text-center
			.col-sm-3.col-sm-offset-2
				button.btn.btn-link(type="submit") Log In
			.col-sm-1
				a(href="/")
					img(src="images/dc_roasters_200x124_lt.png")
			.col-sm-3
				button.btn.btn-link(type="submit") Register
	div.container-fluid
		.row.header
			.col-sm-12
				h2 A better way to grind
				h5 Freshly roasted coffee beans delivered weekly to your door.
		.row.how
			.col-sm-12.text-center
				p How It Works
		.row
			#step-one.col-sm-12.steps
				h3.title 1. We get the coffee
				p Each bean is hand selected
				p Each bean is measured for precise size
				p Each bean is tenderly caressed
				.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-6.arrow-holder
					.arrow-down
		.row
			#step-two.col-sm-12.steps
				.col-sm-2
					img(src="images/grower.jpg")
				.col-sm-9
					h3 2. We pick up the coffee
					p  We place the coffee in bags
					p  Each bag is transported in climate-controlled trucks
					p  Every six hours the bags are rotated to keep the beans uniform and delicious
				.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-6.arrow-holder
					.arrow-down
		.row
			#step-three.col-sm-12.steps
				img(src="images/cupSteam.jpg")
				h3 3. You drink the coffee
				p The coffee tastes delicious
				p You want more coffee!!
				p Get it NOW!
				.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-6.arrow-holder
					.arrow-down
		.row
			#get-started.col-sm-12
				a(href="/register")
					button.btn.btn-primary(type="button") Get Started




